description:
For the Lin Kuei, at any cost. Sektor joins #MK1 when Khaos Reigns launches September 24.

Mortal Kombat 1: Khaos Reigns expands Liu Kang’s New Era with a new story campaign and an all-new cinematic experience. Discover how Liu Kang rallies his champions and puts faith in his enemies as he battles the ruthless Titan Havik, who threatens to plunge the realms into khaos. If they fail, the New Era will be reduced to anarchy.

description:
In this gameplay, Princess Zelda escapes from a dungeon and uses her Tri Rod to make Echoes and battle everything from Moblins and Strandtula's to a Talus and Dark Link. Echoes of Wisdom involves a lot of puzzle-solving by copying both monsters and everyday objects and then using them creatively in a physics-based environment.

#gaming #thelegendofzeldaechoesofwisdom #gamespot
title: Ten Minutes Of The Legend of Zelda: Echoes of Wisdom Gameplay

description:
Princess Zelda takes a starring role for the first time in the franchise that bears her name, with a suite of ingenious and creative powers to play with.

Although it shares the extremely cute, diorama-esque aesthetic of its top-down predecessor Link's Awakening, Echoes of Wisdom captures much more of the systemic and improvisational joys of Breath of the Wild and Tears of the Kingdom than you might expect.

#gaming #legendofzeldaechoesofwisdom #gamespot
title: Zelda: Echoes of Wisdom Plays Like A Mini Tears Of The Kingdom
